Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sampleapp.dto.Group

  • public class Group
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a Group Object of the WAAD top level entity Group. Also this class gives a publicly available access mechanism to access each individual member variables such as Object Id, DisplayName etc.
